{"word":"G3875 - παράκλητος - paráklētos - par-ak'-lay-tos - Advocate","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παράκλητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>paráklētos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>par-ak'-lay-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Advocate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தேற்றரவாளன், நீதிபரர் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. one who pleads another's case before a judge, a pleader, counsel for defense, legal assistant; an advocate:"},{"paragraph":"2. an intercessor"},{"paragraph":"3. a helper, succorer, aider, assistant"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> An <i>intercessor</i>, <i>consoler:</i> - advocate, comforter."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3870 - παρακαλέω - parakaléō - par-ak-al-eh'-o/3870\">G3870</a>, <a href=\"#/G3874 - παράκλησις - paráklēsis - par-ak'-lay-sis/3874\">G3874</a>, <a href=\"#/G3875 - παράκλητος - paráklētos - par-ak'-lay-tos/3875\">G3875</a>, <a href=\"#/G870 - ἀφόβως - aphóbōs - af-ob'-oce/870\">G870</a>"}]}